7 (9) For the purposes of this section:
8 (a) "accessory dwelling unit" means a self-contained living unit on the same parcel as a single-
9 family dwelling of greater square footage that includes its own cooking, sleeping, and sanitation facilities and
10 complies with or is otherwise exempt from any applicable building code, fire code, and public health and safety
